  "description": [
    "Page 2 EDITORIALS Resignation Unaccepted Dear Mrs Mabel Marks We appreciate your offer of resignation as the Westside Enterprises Cashion correspon dent We recognize the circum stances which prompted your offer A telephone caller threatened some vague reprisals against the Enterprise if you continued in your position because of your interest in a local political mat ter the upcoming election which will determine whether the Lit tleton school district shall be governed by a three or five man board of trustees We know you would like to continue as our correspondent for Cashion And we believe that never before or since has any newspaper given such com plete coverage of Cashion af fairs as has the Enterprise dur ing your tenure as our repre sentative in Cashion We resent threats against this newspaper and against its repre sentatives We are incensed at the effrontery of an individual who thinks an idle word will rid him of opposition and the stu pidity of an individual who cant keep his issues straight Our Moneys Worth We all know that we never get our moneys worth in the expenditure of tax dollars and with the tremendous tax burden we carry these days it"
  ],
